cs.LG, cs.GT, cs.AI, cs.DS, cs.SI 

The paper deals with clustering, which is a common topic in machine learning and data science. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) are likely categories. The paper also uses cooperative game theory concepts, which suggests that it could belong to cs.GT (Computer Science and Game Theory) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Finally, the paper's focus on clustering patterns could also place it in cs.SI (Social and Information Networks).
